User Story:
  ☐ Create a static app, i will give app name.
  ☐ Create a dynamic app, i will give app name.
  ☐ Rotate the secret key for my platform. this is for signing the request.
  ☐ Deploy an app, i will pass the api key, secret key. You have to sign and upload.
  ☐ List all my apps.
  ☐ If my application logs then it should be availble in logs section.
  ☐ Add app secret variables.

Flow:
  ☐ When an app is deployed, it should create a version and store it in db and volume.  maintain the progress of deployment.
    

Non Functional Requirements:
  ☐ only one deployment at a time for a given app.
  ☐ restrict number of ongoing deployment. (openresty rate limit)
  ☐ Only one root user
  ☐ Should we keep root user and other users separate in the db?



